<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="icon" href="/F.png" type="image/x-icon">
    <title>About FixMe</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/animate.css/4.1.1/animate.min.css">
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #F3F4F6, #D1D5DB);
            color: #333;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .head {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;
        }

        h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 2em;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 20px 0;
        }

        p {
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .image-container {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .image-container img {
            max-width: 100%;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        
    /* Keyframe animation */
    @keyframes fadeInUp {
      from {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(20px);
      }
      to {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
      }
    }

    /* Additional styles */
    .graphic {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    .graphic img {
      max-width: 100%;
    }

    .animation {
      animation: pulse 2s infinite;
    }

        ul {
            padding-left: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        li {
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        strong {
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .custom-shape-divider-bottom {
            margin-top: 20px;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #F3F4F6, #D1D5DB);
            overflow: hidden;
            height: 100px;
        }

        .custom-shape-divider-bottom svg {
            position: relative;
            display: block;
            width: calc(100% + 1.3px);
            height: 100%;
            transform: rotateY(180deg);
            z-index: 1;
        }

    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container animate__animated animate__fadeIn">
        <div class="head">
            <h1>About FixMe</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Welcome to FixMe, your trusted partner in the journey of career growth and development. At FixMe, we understand the importance of finding the right job and building meaningful professional connections. Our platform is designed to empower individuals like you to navigate the complex job market with confidence and clarity.</p>
            <h2>Our Mission</h2>
            <div class="image-container">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1541746972996-4e0b0f43e02a?q=80&w=1470&auto=format&fit=crop&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D" alt="">
            </div>
            <p>Our mission at FixMe is to revolutionize the job search experience by providing personalized recommendations tailored to your skills, preferences, and career goals. We believe that everyone deserves to find a job that not only fulfills their professional aspirations but also brings joy and fulfillment to their lives.</p>
            <h2>How We Work</h2>
            <p>FixMe utilizes cutting-edge technology and innovative algorithms to analyze your unique profile and deliver curated job suggestions that match your individual needs. Say goodbye to the overwhelm of sifting through endless job postings and hello to opportunities that are perfectly tailored for you.</p>
            <h2>Our Community</h2>
            <p>FixMe is more than just a job search platform – we're a supportive community of professionals dedicated to helping each other succeed. Through our blog, workshops, and networking events, we provide valuable insights, tips, and resources to help you navigate every step of your career journey.</p>
            <h2>Why Choose FixMe?</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Personalized Recommendations:</strong> Receive job suggestions tailored to your skills, preferences, and career goals.</li>
                <li><strong>Expert Guidance:</strong> Access resources, workshops, and expert advice to enhance your job search strategy.</li>
                <li><strong>Community Support:</strong> Connect with like-minded professionals, share insights, and build valuable networks.</li>
                <li><strong>Continuous Improvement:</strong> We're committed to continuously enhancing our platform to better serve your needs and deliver an exceptional user experience.</li>
            </ul>
            <h2>Join Us Today</h2>
            <div class="graphic">
                <img src="/favicon final.png" alt="Graphic" class="animation">
              </div>
            <p>Ready to take the next step in your career journey? Join FixMe today and let's embark on this exciting adventure together. Whether you're a recent graduate, a mid-career professional, or a seasoned expert, FixMe is here to help you achieve your career aspirations and unlock your full potential. Welcome to FixMe – where every opportunity is within reach.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="custom-shape-divider-bottom">
        <svg data-name="Layer 1" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 1200 120" preserveAspectRatio="none">
            <path d="M1200 0L0 0 598.67 114.34 1200 0z" fill="#ffffff"></path>
        </svg>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
